reviewText: Basic instruction on casting and good tips. I actually found them hilarious in a good dorky way. It was a bit dated but there is good information. Still wondering why his assistant put a pen I his hand lol
The DVD would not work in my DVD player, x box one or laptop. Don't waste your money.
I have learned so much with the DVDS. I LOVE this line of DVDs.
Great how-to instruction on how to cast a clay sculpture in plaster to make a latex mask. I still use the knowledge today.
